properties.areaDesc: Guadalupe Mountains Above 7000 Feet; Guadalupe and Delaware Mountains; Guadalupe Mountains of Eddy County
properties.headline: High Wind Watch issued January 26 at 2:39AM CST until January 27 at 8:00PM CST by NWS Midland/Odessa TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 35 to 45 mph with gusts up to 60 mph
possible.

* WHERE...Guadalupe and Delaware Mountains.

* WHEN...From late Monday morning through Monday evening.

* IMPACTS...Travel will be difficult, especially for high profile
vehicles. Low flying light aircraft may experience severe
turbulence near the mountains.
properties.instruction:
Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this
situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe
location prior to the onset of winds.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WATCH IN EFFECT FROM MONDAY MORNING THROUGH MONDAY EVENING
